rmulas and traps. Absolutely best product I've found and I've tried a bunch.\u003c/p\u003e","purchase_date":"March 14th, 2024","rating":5,"show_purchase_date":false,"show_stars":true,"title":"","verified":true},"type":"testimonial"},"testimonial_JF4Nkz":{"settings":{"author_name":"Amanda \u0026 Chris T.","avatar_image":"shopify://shop_images/download_22.png","content":"\u003cp\u003eMy husband and I purchased these fly traps to help cut down on some of the flies in our yard. These traps worked better than we expected. We were shocked to find we were filling up a bag every 1 to 2 days. We absolutely see a decrease in flies in our yard.\u003c/p\u003e","purchase_date":"March 14th, 2024","rating":5,"show_purchase_date":false,"show_stars":true,"title":"","verified":true},"type":"testimonial"},"testimonial_JXbXQW":{"settings":{"author_name":"Dale W.","avatar_image":"shopify://shop_images/download_17.png","content":"\u003cp\u003eThese things stink like crazy so do not hang close to the house. It does however solve a lot of the summer fly problem we have in the south. So the smell is awful, but the flies love it. You have to pick the battle for yourself.\u003c/p\u003e","purchase_date":"March 14th, 2024","rating":5,"show_purchase_date":false,"show_stars":true,"title":"","verified":true},"type":"testimonial"},"testimonial_T3abPn":{"settings":{"author_name":"Lisa M.","avatar_image":"shopify://shop_images/download_11.png","content":"\u003cp\u003eI have been dealing with flies! We are rural and there is a chicken farm about 1.5 miles away. It's rough. Trust me. I was complaining to a neighbor and she said to get the fly bags. OMG! I thought they weren't going to work. Wrong. They are amazing. Over the last 2 months, our house has been nearly fly-free. It's a game changer.\u003c/p\u003e","purchase_date":"March 14th, 2024","rating":5,"show_purchase_date":false,"show_stars":true,"title":"","verified":true},"type":"testimonial"},"testimonial_XBRibJ":{"settings":{"author_name":"Mike D.","avatar_image":"shopify://shop_images/download_20.png","content":"\u003cp\u003eWe camp all summer and of course the flies do too. We had tried many types and brands of fly deterrents but they weren't much help. You just add water and hang them up. To remove it, just take it down, screw down the top and toss it in the trash. You will be shocked how many flies it catches.\u003c/p\u003e","purchase_date":"March 14th, 2024","rating":5,"show_purchase_date":false,"show_stars":true,"title":"","verified":true},"type":"testimonial"},"testimonial_a4TUmV":{"settings":{"author_name":"Sharon L.","avatar_image":"shopify://shop_images/download_21.png","content":"\u003cp\u003eWe have been using these for 4 summers and these keep the flies away from the folks swimming in our pool. They stink when full — but they are full. We take them down and put up a new set.\u003c/p\u003e","purchase_date":"March 14th, 2024","rating":5,"show_purchase_date":false,"show_stars":true,"title":"","verified":true},"type":"testimonial"},"testimonial_cEQBtg":{"settings":{"author_name":"Tammy R.","avatar_image":"shopify://shop_images/download_12.png","content":"\u003cp\u003eI live in Southern Alabama and the flies are a plenty. I have dogs and dog poop just attracts flies, no matter how fast you scoop the poop. I've tried everything to help reduce the flies and this is the only fly catcher that works.\u003c/p\u003e","purchase_date":"March 14th, 2024","rating":5,"show_purchase_date":false,"show_stars":true,"title":"","verified":true},"type":"testimonial"},"testimonial_cVrT8K":{"settings":{"author_name":"Karen S.","avatar_image":"shopify://shop_images/download_14.png","content":"\u003cp\u003eI live near a horse pasture and have chickens too. Flies abound in my world, hence the traps. They work! They work so well! Works well on blue bottle flies and house flies. Buy these traps. Wage war on the flies.\u003c/p\u003e","purchase_date":"March 14th, 2024","rating":5,"show_purchase_date":false,"show_stars":true,"title":"","verified":true},"type":"testimonial"},"testimonial_gTFi6W":{"settings":{"author_name":"Greg H.","avatar_image":"shopify://shop_images/download_15.png","content":"\u003cp\u003eI set one of these up in my yard, close enough so I could see it, but not smell it. After just a few minutes there it had flies all over. After two days, hundreds of them are in the water. I've not had a problem with them on my deck since I put this up.\u003c/p\u003e","purchase_date":"March 14th, 2024","rating":5,"show_purchase_date":false,"show_stars":true,"title":"","verified":true},"type":"testimonial"}},"name":"Testimonials","settings":{"accent_color":"#ef4a65","accent_font_family":"inherit","accent_font_style":"normal","accent_font_weight":"inherit","accent_text_gradient":"linear-gradient(45deg, rgba(239, 74, 101, 1), rgba(255, 107, 157, 1) 100%)","accent_text_margin_left":0,"anchor_id":"","author_avatar_text_size":12,"author_info_bg_color":"#f8f8f8","author_info_border_color":"#e5e5e5","author_info_border_radius":50,"author_info_border_style":"solid","author_info_border_width":1,"author_name_size":12,"avatar_color":"#b1b1b1","avatar_text_color":"#000000","card_background":"#f9f9f9","card_border_color":"#f9f9f9","card_border_radius":5,"card_border_style":"solid","card_border_width":1,"card_gap":28,"card_rating_size":16,"card_text_color":"#6b6b6b","card_width_desktop":340,"card_width_mobile":75,"dot_color":"#b6974c","enable_author_info_border":false,"enable_card_border":true,"enable_mask_fade":true,"enable_rating_summary_border":true,"heading":"","heading_accent":"","heading_color":"#141720","heading_line_height":1.2,"heading_size":44,"heading_size_mobile":28,"heading_tag":"h2","individual_card_height":true,"nav_button_bg":"#ffffff","nav_button_border":"#191919","nav_button_color":"#141720","nav_button_radius":25,"override_global_accent":true,"padding_bottom":20,"padding_top":20,"purchase_date_color":"#666666","purchase_date_icon_color":"#666666","purchase_date_prefix":"Purchased 